data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom brick home with a 2-car detached garage! Located in a desirable neighborhood, this property offers a blend of timeless elegance and modern convenience, making it the perfect place to call home. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide comfort and privacy. Each room offers plenty of space for rest and relaxation, with ample closet space to keep belongings organized. The full bathroom is stylishly designed and includes a bathtub shower combination. Step outside to the beautifully landscaped backyard, where you'll find the 2-car detached garage. This versatile space not only provides secure parking for your vehicles but can also be utilized as a workshop or additional storage area. Situated on a generously sized lot, this home offers plenty of outdoor space for recreation and entertainment. Imagine spending warm summer evenings hosting barbecues, gardening, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your own private oasis. Don't miss out!
